ement\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The fallout from the controversywill have far reaching and immediate consequences for Team GB inParis, as well their three-time gold medalist, but in the long-term animal rights group PETA are adamant that equestrian events are outdated and should have no place in the Games.\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 622, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 433, \"end\": 440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999690321606, \"rank\": 3.0954026989313494e-08, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 553, \"end\": 563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.6050968871707554, \"rank\": 0.6526278766679314, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The fallout\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 358}, {\"ngram\": \"the controversywill\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 383}, {\"ngram\": \"far reaching and immediate consequences\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 428}, {\"ngram\": \"as well their three-time gold medalist\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 488}, {\"ngram\": \"the long-term animal rights group PETA\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 535}, {\"ngram\": \"no place\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 608}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 621}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The message to the International Olympic Committee should be clear by now: remove equestrian events from the Olympic Games,' a statement read.\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 644, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\