 \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2691}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2722}, {\"ngram\": \"this process\", \"from\": 2731, \"to\": 2743}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What happened was completely out of character and does not reflect how I train my horses or coach my pupils, however there is no excuse.\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2894, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"character\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2803}, {\"ngram\": \"my horses\", \"from\": 2837, \"to\": 2846}, {\"ngram\": \"my pupils\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2865}, {\"ngram\": \"no excuse\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am deeply ashamed and should have set a better example in that moment.\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2967, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a better example\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 2951}, {\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 2966}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sincerely sorry for my actions and devastated that I have let everyone down, including Team GB, fans and sponsors.\", \"from\": 2969, \"to\": 3088, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3061, \"end\": 3068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999690321606, \"rank\": 3.0954026989313494e-08, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my actions\", \"from\": 2994, \"to\": 3004}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3044}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 3070, \"to\": 3074}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsors\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3087}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will cooperate fully with the FEI, British Equestrian Federation and British Dressage during their investigations, and will not be commenting further until the process is complete.\", \"from\": 3090, \"to\": 3272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3122, \"end\": 3125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8600124325584696e-30, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 3127, \"end\": 3156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Equestrian Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 3161, \"end\": 3177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Dressage\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their investigations\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3205}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 3248, \"to\": 3259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Charlotte Dujardin, 23rd July 2024.\", \"from\": 3274, \"to\": 3309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3274, \"end\": 3292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charlotte Dujardin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Upon receiving the video, the FEI promptly initiated an investigation.\", \"from\": 3311, \"to\": 3382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3342, \"end\": 3345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8600124325584696e-30, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid